data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat in Spring Creek, just outside of Hot Springs, NC. This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom private home offers the perfect blend of seclusion and convenience, with just a short 25-minute drive to downtown Hot Springs for all your shopping and dining needs. Nestled in a serene & tranquil setting just across the street from the rippling Spring Creek, this property promises a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of city life with over 3 acres of privacy. A full brick ranch home that exudes classic charm. There is a living room, formal dining room, large kitchen, and then a comfortable den area with gas log fireplace. 3 bedrooms and a full hall bath complete the main level. The partially finished basement has ample room for either a large family room or bonus room with 2nd full bath on one side, and on the other side, plenty of space in the unfinished portion for a workshop &garage. Tucked into the valley, make this your year-round home or a weekend getaway.
